trans-unit.source: Stores objects that represent the static methods of the <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.RegExpPrototype"></xref> class.
The <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.LenientRegExpPrototype"></xref> class belongs to the built-in object model category.

Stores an object that represents the static <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.RegExpPrototype.compile(System.Object,System.Object,System.Object)"></xref> method of the <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.RegExpPrototype"></xref> class.
Stores a reference to a <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.RegExpConstructor"></xref> object.

Stores an object that represents the static <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.RegExpPrototype.exec(System.Object,System.Object)"></xref> method of the <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.RegExpPrototype"></xref> class.

Stores an object that represents the static <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.RegExpPrototype.test(System.Object,System.Object)"></xref> method of the <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.RegExpPrototype"></xref> class.
Stores an object that represents the static <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.RegExpPrototype.toString(System.Object)"></xref> method of the <xref href="Microsoft.JScript.RegExpPrototype"></xref> class.
